des:
Apone Smart products help you control home appliance. You can simply ask Alexa to turn on or turn off your device.
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust your device- just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show.

After connecting Alexa to your Apone Smart products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Apone Smart" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one Apone Smart account in our "Apone Smart" app;
(3). You need to have some Apone Smart devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "Apone Smart" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Apone Smart" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Apone Smart" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Apone Smart", and you'll be navigated to Apone Smart login page;
(9). Input your Apone Smart account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa,turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa,turn off the bedroom light.”
“Alexa,set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa,brighten the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa,dim the bedroom light to 50%.”
"Alexa, set bedroom light to green."
"Alexa, set bedroom light to cool white."
